Review: Felt so on edge the whole movie. The ability of humans to adapt and survive is insane! I cannot imagine how it must have felt to be saved after freezing and starving for months. Feel like this was really well done and respectful of all the people involved. Definitely warrants a delicious hour-long Wikipedia deep-dive now

how could these people live right next door?
